ern.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 0aSpirituality in literature. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Renaissance.2bisacsh  aBunyan.  aDonne.  aEarly modern literature.  aMarvell.  aMilton.  aReformation.  aRenaissance.  aasceticism.  aausterity.  abody/soul.  aearly modern literature.  apoetry.  areligion.  aself-denial.  aself.  athe body.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDTL Humanities 2020z978311073776908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020 Englishz978311070474708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020z9783110704532oZDB-23-DKU08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUTP eBook-Package Pilot 2019z978311065206240uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/978148753199740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781487531997423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781487531997.jpg  a978-3-11-065206-2  UTP eBook-Package Pilot 2019b2019  a978-3-11-070471-6  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070474-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-073776-9  DTL Humanities 2020b2020  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-DKUb2020